{"tid":1838102,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"澳門宣布學校延至2月10日或之後上課","createTime":"2020-01-24T01:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T08:22:14.000Z","uid":41404,"like":295,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":113,"replies":[{"pid":"4483d8d7dcf479935fa02db2046ec7132aca51f1","tid":1838102,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:54:05.000Z","msg":"澳門教育暨青年局宣布，因應新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情，非高等教育學校在農曆新年假期後，延至2月10日或之後上課。<br />\n<br />\n澳門當局表示，已通知學校妥善安排學生在家學習的相應方案，私立補充教學輔助中心及持續教育機構同時亦應配合，即延至下月10日或之後運作。<br />\n<br />\n當局亦指，會持續密切監察疫情發展，適時作出相應安排。"},{"pid":"7ed79aa01f1ad4ff8fbd63f05b20e955fca05f7d","tid":1838102,"uid":162008,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:55:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"5cfb6dfe2bdb86129329cb8710c638955a821844","tid":1838102,"uid":6548,"like":85,"dislike":1,"score":84,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:55:44.000Z","msg":"香港表示考慮下去唔去支那旅行啦<br />\n一定唔停課 一間中圈套"},{"pid":"c2aa3259d128c34b11966be087c58a174547a1d6","tid":1838102,"uid":997,"like":190,"dislike":1,"score":189,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:55:47.000Z","msg":"林奠 : 我係唔會中計"},{"pid":"0e439004e2a0aacdb83a62e7cf5e912d1feaaf6e","tid":1838102,"uid":216163,"like":135,"dislike":2,"score":133,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:56:48.000Z","msg":"澳門真係好識安穩人心..."},{"pid":"0904c2967fad56bbea1e25a4e621a8af2279d661","tid":1838102,"uid":64191,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:57:49.000Z","msg":"澳門咁細，有事既權貴商賈都會一獲熟"},{"pid":"cdcf67ac10557b9308c679881bcd4ab9dca0e483